            <title>[SOLR-2390] Performance of usePhraseHighlighter is terrible on very large Documents, regardless of hl.maxDocCharsToAnalyze</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2390</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a large performance bug here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12499872">SOLR-2390</key>
            <summary>Performance of usePhraseHighlighter is terrible on very large Documents, regardless of hl.maxDocCharsToAnalyze</summary>
